      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64, unknown/unknown: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/decdd900-a020-11e4-b032-5254006e85c2).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
