      "date": "2015-01-19 21:25:06.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nSeems fine to me.\n\n \nq:~# export MDSCOUNT=4\nq:~# llmount.sh \n...\nq:~# cd /mnt/lustre\nq:lustre# mkdir d0\nq:lustre# lfs setdirstripe -c4 d0/d1\nq:lustre# createmany -o d0/d1/f 1024\ntotal: 1024 creates in 2.05 seconds: 499.75 creates/second\nq:lustre# lfs find --size +8k d0/d1/\nd0/d1/\nq:lustre# dirs=$(lfs find --size +8k d0/d1/)\nq:lustre# [ -n \"$dirs\" ] || echo XXX\nq:lustre#\n\nI'll add the test.",
